DESCRIPTION
.br
.in +6
The
.ul 1
msg_portname()
system service returns the
.ul 1
port_name
associated with an open port, suitable for use in
a later call to
.ul 1
msg_connect().
It is most often used to find out if two open files
reside on the same "filesystem", that is, under
the same server.
